@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@username = {{$dotenv GUBEE_SECURITY_USER}}
@password = {{$dotenv GUBEE_SECURITY_PASSWORD}}
@accountId = account-001
@sku = ABC-123
@eventId = evt-http-001

### Health publico
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger-ui.html

### OpenAPI JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/api-docs

### Processar evento REST com Basic Auth
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "type": "STOCK_ADJUSTED",
  "occurredAt": "2026-05-28T10:00:00Z",
  "accountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "sku": "{{sku}}",
  "available": 10,
  "reason": "manual_adjustment"
}

### Consultar saldo atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stocks/{{accountId}}/{{sku}}

### Consultar historico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stocks/{{accountId}}/{{sku}}/history

### Consultar evento processado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/{{eventId}}

### Metrica de eventos processados
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/metrics/stock.events.processed
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}
